  "title": "OPERATION EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities：</strong></p><ul><li>Support daily operations to ensure smooth and efficient business activities</li><li>Assist in coordinating on-site operations, including customer service and floor support</li><li>Carry out basic administrative and operational tasks as assigned</li><li>Support promotional activities, on-site recruitment, and simple marketing initiatives when required</li><li>Coordinate with different departments to ensure operational requirements are met</li><li>Monitor operational issues and report to supervisors promptly</li><li>Ensure compliance with company policies, procedures, and workplace rules</li><li>Perform any other duties assigned by management from time to time</li></ul><p><p><strong>Job Requirements：</strong></p><ul><li><strong> </strong>Minimum Secondary School or equivalent qualification</li></ul><ul><li><p>No prior working experience required; training will be provided</p></li><li><p>Willing to perform shift work, including weekends and public holidays (24-hour operation)</p></li><li><p>Able to communicate in basic English; Mandarin is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Positive working attitude, responsible, and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently as well as in a team</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with on-site and hands-on operational work</p></li><li><p>Physically fit to stand and move during working hours</p></li><li><p>Able to follow company policies, procedures, and instructions</p></li></ul></p>",
